Title: Best Friends, Same Ends
Description:
I saw the shipwright leave the cave and head down to the beach. She was accompanied by a formidable looking nerubian.

The shipwright is the mastermind behind this entire operation. She knows precisely how the lumber is to be cut and what lumber is needed for their airships.

The nerubians know this and likely assigned one of their best to protect her.

If we can eliminate the shipwright, we can bring all of their carefully laid plans to ruin.
ObjectivesText: Eliminate Shipwright Isaebela and Shadowspinner Azarak at Silkwood Grotto.
PortraitGiverText: Isaebela provides the Order of Night with lumber to build their own airships.
